Changes in new version

Version KarsTS 2.4 (December 15, 2020)
-------------------------------------------

- Many functions have been adapted to the new version of R without any noticeable changes for the users.
- The plots no longer use the package tkrplot, for this reason the GUI has changed slightly. 
- The User's Guide has been adapted accordingly. 


Version KarsTS 2.3 (June 7, 2020)
-------------------------------------------

- A function to upsample time series was added (the previous version only allowed downsampling)
- Functions to build and plot fixed amount of neighbors recurrence matrices were added.
- Now the user can choose the resolution that will be used when saving the plots to image files. 
- The examples were edited. 
- The button MCAR Little's test was removed


